snippet.title: Delivery Quest - Deliver the package and escape the giant cursed sword!
snippet.description:
Play for free on itch.io https://r-goulart.itch.io/delivery-quest?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt You are Amina, an explorer who works as a courier for the Fireball Express company. She has a curse and every time she goes on a mission a giant cursed sword comes out to attack her - but in some cases it can be useful too.

➡️ More from Róger Goulart https://r-goulart.itch.io/?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
➡️ More games with pixel art https://itch.io/games/tag-pixel-art?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
